contents.main: If You don't like me its okay, I was'nt born to impress you
Down to earth, but still above you
I'm an odd combination of REALLY SWEET and DON'T MESS WITH ME.

When you feel like quiting , think about why you started
Don't stop until you are proud of yourself

If you don’t control your attitude, then it will control you.
Your opinions about me do not change who I am.

I am prettier than your ex 😍
and hotter than your next😙😘.
